nodes.text: The father Dathomiri Witch Kaminne and Olianne Sihn was a male Dathomirian. They belonged to the Raining Leaves Clan on the planet Dathomir.
In 33 ABY, an uprising of the clan's male slaves occurred which resulted in the deaths of over two-thirds of the clan's population. Sihn's father was among those who perished.
